---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me — hkg">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-10 animate-fade-up">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">About Me</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500">The long version.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="aspect-[3/1] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-10">
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1499750310107-5fef28a66643?w=900&q=85"
        alt="workspace"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover brightness-75"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Hey — I'm hkg. I build things, read things, and spend a lot of time
        thinking about how people spend their time.
      </p>
      <p>
        I grew up curious. The kind of kid who took apart everything just to see
        how it worked — and occasionally put it back together. That curiosity
        never really left. It just got more structured over time, pointed in the
        direction of software, systems, and the messy, fascinating problem of
        how humans interact with technology.
      </p>
      <p>
        I care about building things that are genuinely useful — not just clever
        or shiny. I have a soft spot for good writing, long walks, and physical
        books. I believe most problems can be solved by thinking slowly and
        working patiently.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-neutral-800 pt-8 mt-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">What I'm Doing Now</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-sm text-neutral-400">
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-neutral-700 shrink-0">—</span>
          Building this website, apparently.
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-neutral-700 shrink-0">—</span>
          Reading more than I probably should.
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-neutral-700 shrink-0">—</span>
          Trying to spend less time on the internet (see: <a
            href="/get-off-the-phones"
            class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors"
            >GET OFF THE PHONES</a
          >).
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-2">
          <span class="text-neutral-700 shrink-0">—</span>
          Cooking more at home, mostly succeeding.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-neutral-800 pt-8 mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Interests</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {
          [
            "software",
            "reading",
            "travel",
            "long-form journalism",
            "urban design",
            "cooking",
            "film",
            "running",
            "history",
            "design systems",
          ].map((tag) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-neutral-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-neutral-400">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-neutral-800 pt-8 mt-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">The honest version</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          I overthink things more than I should and underprepare for things more
          than I'd like. I make good coffee and occasionally give advice that
          turns out to be useful. I'm better in writing than in person, but I'm
          working on it. I believe the internet peaked sometime around 2008 and
          we've been slowly losing something ever since — hence <a
            href="/get-off-the-phones"
            class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors"
            >this</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you've read this far, you're probably a little like me. In which
          case: hello, and welcome.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
